---
import Feature from '../../layouts/Feature.astro';
import { keys } from '../../lib/keybindings';
---

<Feature
  title="POWER FEATURES"
  subtitle="Smart paste protection and additional productivity tools."
>
  <h2>Smart Paste</h2>
  <p>ori-term protects you from accidental pastes that could cause damage:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Multi-line paste warning</strong> — asks for confirmation before pasting content that spans multiple lines</li>
    <li><strong>Large paste confirmation</strong> — warns before pasting unusually large content</li>
    <li><strong>Configurable</strong> — set to Always, Auto (respects bracketed paste mode), or Never</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Smart Copy / Paste</h2>
  <p><kbd>{keys.smartCopy}</kbd> copies if there is an active selection, otherwise sends the normal Ctrl+C (SIGINT) to the shell. <kbd>{keys.smartPaste}</kbd> pastes from clipboard. Explicit <kbd>{keys.copy}</kbd> / <kbd>{keys.paste}</kbd> are always available.</p>

  <h2>Select All</h2>
  <p><kbd>{keys.selectAll}</kbd> selects intelligently: if shell integration detects you are at a prompt, it selects the command input line. Otherwise it selects the entire buffer.</p>

  <h2>Prompt Navigation</h2>
  <p>Jump between shell prompts with <kbd>{keys.previousPrompt}</kbd> and <kbd>{keys.nextPrompt}</kbd>. Requires shell integration (OSC 133) to mark prompt boundaries.</p>

  <h2>Settings UI</h2>
  <p>Press <kbd>{keys.openSettings}</kbd> to open the settings overlay. Change color schemes, adjust opacity, toggle blur, and configure rendering options — all without editing config files.</p>

  <div class="roadmap-banner">
    <strong>Additional power features are planned:</strong>
    <p>Command palette, Quake-style quick terminal, terminal inspector, desktop notifications, and taskbar progress indicators are on the <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '')}/roadmap`}>roadmap</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Feature>

<style>
  .roadmap-banner {
    border: var(--border-weight) solid var(--accent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 8%, transparent);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .roadmap-banner strong {
    color: var(--accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .roadmap-banner p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
</style>
